{"tid":985827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛津大學暫停接受華為捐款","createTime":"2019-01-18T03:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T03:15:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8445e3bf1feadd2ea845a58941899f1f24384ea","tid":985827,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190118/s00005/b3b06943b5dea64b882ed195c9a124b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2Fb3b06943b5dea64b882ed195c9a124b5.jpg&h=4488680c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學本月8日決定，暫停接受中國電訊巨頭華為的捐款和贊助。校方表示，該決定適用於研究合約資助和慈善捐贈。華為發言人指，公司暫未獲牛津大學的有關通知。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學解釋，決定是基於英國近月與華為的夥伴關係引來公眾關注，校方希望有關問題能盡快解決。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學指，將會繼續現有已獲得或已承諾由華為資助的研究，透露校內目前有兩個相關項目，當中華為的資助金額為69.2萬英鎊（約705萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190118/s00005/1547778225123/牛津大學暫停接受華為捐款\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2F1547778225123%2F%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE&d=fU3nvaAexaWFGJTF6lGlK2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=93bf2fb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2F1547778225123%2F%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE&h=7aac144b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190118/s00005/1547778225123/牛津大學暫停接受華為捐款</a>"},{"pid":"488526136565e7852f5e9561169f5874a75426ae","tid":985827,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f0e5f4b0745bfad12990f0957154ca34f3eb339","tid":985827,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"7百幾萬啫